00:07:09.209 --> 00:07:10.689
I'm thinking of selling it.
 

00:07:10.689 --> 00:07:18.740
Does anybody have any--does
anybody need a watch?

00:07:18.740 --> 00:07:22.089
You do?
 

00:07:22.089 --> 00:07:23.879
You don't?
 

00:07:23.879 --> 00:07:29.680
What does a standard Movado
watch sell for in a jewelry

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:30.540
store?
 

00:07:30.540 --> 00:07:34.329
I actually don't know.
 

00:07:34.329 --> 00:07:35.430
I should have done my homework.
 

00:07:35.430 --> 00:07:41.608
I think its low hundreds and
