00:47:23.070 --> 00:47:29.699
Okay I'll do it.
 

00:47:29.699 --> 00:47:37.518
The system of property is built
on nation states.

00:47:37.518 --> 00:47:39.480
Nation states are the
underlying unit.

00:47:39.480 --> 00:47:45.144
When you have a frontier
society, which the United States

00:47:45.144 --> 00:47:50.530
remained until about 1880,
you have a vast area where

00:47:50.530 --> 00:47:56.563
there is effectively no state or
if there is a state it is a very

00:47:56.563 --> 00:48:01.559
weak state with very limited
capacities to enforce any

00:48:01.559 --> 00:48:03.539
property system.
 

00:48:03.539 --> 00:48:06.791
The key Green v.
 

00:48:06.791 --> 00:48:13.639
Bittle case,
which arose in Kentucky,

00:48:13.639 --> 00:48:18.090
asserted the following.
 

00:48:18.090 --> 00:48:22.119
It said informal property
rights count for nothing,

00:48:22.119 --> 00:48:27.074
only formal property rights
issued by a part of the United

00:48:27.074 --> 00:48:30.072
States Government,
at either the federal or the

00:48:30.072 --> 00:48:32.250
state level,
count as real.

00:48:32.250 --> 00:48:38.530
This provoked a rebellion that
included violence.

00:48:38.530 --> 00:48:43.659
It also created an enormous
inefficiency because the

00:48:43.659 --> 00:48:48.791
existing informal system of
property rights based on

00:48:48.791 --> 00:48:54.527
preemption and occupation,
so called Tomahawk rights or

00:48:54.527 --> 00:48:57.525
cornfield rights;
you occupy the land,

00:48:57.525 --> 00:49:00.619
improve the land,
demonstrate that you're making

00:49:00.619 --> 00:49:03.780
a living from the land,
and it becomes yours.

00:49:03.780 --> 00:49:05.909
Homesteading was the name for
it.

00:49:05.909 --> 00:49:14.313
In 1862, The Homestead Act,
adopted into Federal law that

00:49:14.313 --> 00:49:23.469
system of informal law and made
an integration between the two

00:49:23.469 --> 00:49:25.119
levels.
 

00:49:25.119 --> 00:49:36.599
The wealth that was built in
the United States in the--

00:49:36.599 --> 00:49:41.021
in everything outside the
original East Coast colonies is

00:49:41.021 --> 00:49:45.760
built up on that peace treaty
between formal and informal.

00:49:45.760 --> 00:49:50.300
The--he does a brilliant job,
de Soto does,

00:49:50.300 --> 00:49:55.009
with the mining camps in
California and with the land

00:49:55.009 --> 00:49:58.360
claim associations in the
Midwest,

00:49:58.360 --> 00:50:00.820
and you can read the details
for yourselves.

00:50:00.820 --> 00:50:06.349
The gist is that a well
functioning system of property

00:50:06.349 --> 00:50:12.715
will have both the formal and
the informal rights in sync with

00:50:12.715 --> 00:50:17.449
one another,
not in tension with one another.

